description:
A new way to collaborate

Empowering teams by messenger, meetings, calendar, docs, and emails. It's all in one place.
Docs
- In viewing mode, AI QuickView provides a concise summary of the document, enabling you to grasp key points at a glance.
Base
- You can use AI to quickly generate relevant options for single option and multiple options fields in Base, making it easier than ever to customize your database.
